Ross Patterson, Jarred Taylor, and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest Tim Kennedy to discuss why schools are rewriting history, how his debate comment on Joe Rogan went global, the state of affairs in today’s in today’s society and if it will change, and how things will shake out for our country after the election. JT also gets his soul crushed by a female TACP who stops by the show.
